originalText.text: Avoid this doctor, his surgical coordinator Taysha & this entire location at all costs. You will truly regret it. Just like me, you will deal with your appointments getting cancelled & rescheduled back to back without being informed. Their lack of communication & organizational skills is horrendous. Also, Dr. Trujillo has showed me some of his work of his patients that he performed rhinoplasty on and each patient either had the same exact nose as before or had a much worse looking nose. He does botched looking noses. They literally look horrible and tragic. You have been warned.
